{"word":"συνευδοκέω","slug":"συνευδοκέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>συνευδοϰέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σύν\">σύν</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εὐδοκέω\">εὐδοκέω</a></el>] ‘join in approving’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of endorsing someone’s activity, in pejorative sense <b>approve, agree with <a href='B:490 11:48'>Lk 11:48</a>; <a href='B:510 8:1'>Ac 8:1</a>; <a href='B:510 22:20'>22:20</a>; <a href='B:520 1:32'>Ro 1:32</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of reaching agreement in a personal matter, <b>agree <a href='B:530 7:12'>1 Cor 7:12f</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:συνετός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:συνευωχέομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}